729664f-a.folder: Victory Boulevard & Forest Avenue, Staten Island, NY
729664f-a.text:
(1)
Silver Lake Park (Staten Island): A scene at dusk across the south basin of the Silver Lake Reservoir.
The view is in a southwesterly direction.
April 29, 1929
P. L. Sperr
(2)
Southwestward across the reservoir from Victory
Boulevard near Forest Avenue.
April 16, 1932
P. L. Sperr
(3)
Wiewing northwestward across the reservoir's north
basin, toward Forest Avenue.
April 16, 1932
P. L. Sperr

729845f-a.folder: Victory Boulevard & Forest Avenue, Staten Island, NY
729845f-a.text:
Victory Boulevard, from Forest Avenue (left) to Woodstock Street, showing on the west side of the Boulevard, in the center of the view, the Jewish Comiunity Center. The view is northwestward across Hero Park, toward the Upper Bay.
April 16, 1932
P. L. Sperr
